{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "pointpoker-api-collection",
    "name": "PointPoker API",
    "description": "Coleção completa da API do PointPoker para testar todas as rotas.\n\n## Fluxo de uso:\n1. **Create Room** — cria sala e retorna `session_token` (host)\n2. **Join Room** — entra na sala com outro nome, retorna outro `session_token`\n3. **Get Room** — consulta estado da sala e participantes\n4. **Start Round** — host inicia rodada de votação (requer `X-Session-Token` do host)\n5. **Cast Vote** — participante vota (requer `X-Session-Token` do participante)\n6. **Get Round State** — consulta estado atual da rodada\n7. **Reveal Votes** — host revela os votos\n8. **Reset Round** — host reseta a rodada\n9. **WebSocket** — conexão WS para eventos em tempo real",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "room_code",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "host_session_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "participant_session_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "round_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "host_participant_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "participant_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Rooms",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Create Room",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 201', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has room and session_token', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('room');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('session_token');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('participant');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Save variables for next requests",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('room_code', jsonData.room.code);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('host_session_token', jsonData.session_token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('host_participant_id', jsonData.participant.id);",
                  "",
                  "console.log('Room Code:', jsonData.room.code);",
                  "console.log('Host Token:', jsonData.session_token);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"Sprint 42 Planning\",\n    \"display_name\": \"Paulo (Host)\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "rooms"]
            },
            "description": "Cria uma nova sala de Planning Poker. Retorna o código da sala e o session_token do host."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Join Room",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has room and session_token', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('room');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('session_token');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('participant');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('participant_session_token', jsonData.session_token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('participant_id', jsonData.participant.id);",
                  "",
                  "console.log('Participant Token:', jsonData.session_token);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"display_name\": \"Maria (Dev)\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/join",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{room_code}}", "join"]
            },
            "description": "Entra em uma sala existente com um nome de exibição. Retorna session_token do participante."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Get Room",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has room and participants', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('room');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('participants');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.participants).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Session tokens are not exposed', function () {",
                  "    jsonData.participants.forEach(function(p) {",
                  "        pm.expect(p.session_token).to.eql('');",
                  "    });",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{room_code}}"]
            },
            "description": "Consulta o estado da sala e lista de participantes. Session tokens não são expostos."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoints de gerenciamento de salas"
    },
    {
      "name": "Voting",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "4. Start Round (Host)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 201', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has round', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('round');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.round).to.have.property('id');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('round_id', jsonData.round.id);",
                  "console.log('Round ID:', jsonData.round.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{host_session_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"story_title\": \"Implementar endpoint de login OAuth\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/rounds",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{room_code}}", "rounds"]
            },
            "description": "Host inicia uma nova rodada de votação com o título da story/task. Requer X-Session-Token do host."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5a. Cast Vote (Host)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has vote', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('vote');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{host_session_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"value\": \"5\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/rounds/{{round_id}}/vote",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "rooms",
                "{{room_code}}",
                "rounds",
                "{{round_id}}",
                "vote"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Host vota na rodada. Valores válidos: 0, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13, 21, ?"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5b. Cast Vote (Participant)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has vote', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('vote');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{participant_session_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"value\": \"8\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/rounds/{{round_id}}/vote",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "rooms",
                "{{room_code}}",
                "rounds",
                "{{round_id}}",
                "vote"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Participante vota na rodada. Valores válidos: 0, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13, 21, ?"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Get Round State",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has round and votes', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('round');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('votes');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Before reveal, vote values should be empty",
                  "if (jsonData.round && jsonData.round.status === 'voting') {",
                  "    pm.test('Vote values are hidden during voting', function () {",
                  "        jsonData.votes.forEach(function(v) {",
                  "            pm.expect(v.value).to.eql('');",
                  "        });",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/rounds/current",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{room_code}}", "rounds", "current"]
            },
            "description": "Consulta o estado da rodada atual. Durante votação, os valores dos votos ficam ocultos."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "7. Reveal Votes (Host)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has votes with values', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('votes');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.votes).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    jsonData.votes.forEach(function(v) {",
                  "        pm.expect(v.value).to.not.eql('');",
                  "        pm.expect(v).to.have.property('display_name');",
                  "    });",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{host_session_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": ""
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/rounds/{{round_id}}/reveal",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "rooms",
                "{{room_code}}",
                "rounds",
                "{{round_id}}",
                "reveal"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Host revela todos os votos da rodada. Após revelar, os valores ficam visíveis."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "8. Reset Round (Host)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Round was reset', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.message).to.eql('round reset');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{host_session_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": ""
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/rounds/{{round_id}}/reset",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "rooms",
                "{{room_code}}",
                "rounds",
                "{{round_id}}",
                "reset"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Host reseta a rodada — limpa todos os votos e volta ao estado de votação."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoints de votação (rounds, votes, reveal, reset)"
    },
    {
      "name": "WebSocket",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "9. WebSocket Connection (info)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/ws?token={{host_session_token}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{room_code}}", "ws"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{host_session_token}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "WebSocket endpoint — use o Postman WebSocket tab ou outra ferramenta WS.\n\nURL: ws://localhost:8080/api/rooms/{{room_code}}/ws?token={{session_token}}\n\nEventos recebidos do servidor:\n- `user_joined` — novo participante entrou\n- `user_left` — participante saiu\n- `round_started` — nova rodada iniciada\n- `vote_cast` — alguém votou (sem valor, apenas indicação)\n- `votes_revealed` — votos revelados (com valores)\n- `round_reset` — rodada resetada\n\nFormato das mensagens:\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"vote_cast\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"participant_id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"display_name\": \"Paulo\",\n    \"has_voted\": true\n  }\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Conexão WebSocket para eventos em tempo real. Use a aba WebSocket do Postman."
    },
    {
